data.description: This 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom home is a single owner non smoking home. It includes a two car garage and lots of storage space. It features a wide open floor plan, walk in closets in three of the four bedrooms, and an on suite with a jetted tub in the master bedroom. All bathrooms include tub and shower features.
